OL,3,C#15bn Covid contracts raise 'profound'
OL,4,Ccorruption concerns, campaigners say
OL,6,FIt also raises concerns about 15
OL,7,Fcontracts worth #1.7 billion awarded
OL,8,Fto politically connected suppliers, a
OL,9,Fsystem deemed unlawful by the high
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,FThe research flags contracts which
OL,13,Fwent to "new inexperienced suppliers,"
OL,14,Fand uncompetitive processes.
OL,16,FIt comes as the Covid-19 Inquiry is
OL,17,Fset to reconvene for its third module,
OL,18,Fexamining the impact of the pandemic
OL,19,Fon the UK's health services.
