OL,6,F"The Covid procurement response was
OL,7,Fmarked by various points of systemic
OL,8,Fweakness and political choices that
OL,9,Fallowed cronyism to thrive, all
OL,10,Fenabled by woefully inadequate public
OL,11,Ftransparency.
OL,13,F"As far as we can ascertain, no other
OL,14,Fcountry used a system like the UK's
OL,15,FVIP lane in their Covid response."
OL,17,FHe urged authorities to "ensure" there
OL,18,Fis "full accountability", as Labour
OL,19,Fministers look to appoint a Covid
OL,20,Fcorruption commissioner.
