OL,6,FIn July, Chancellor Rachel Reeves told
OL,7,Fthe Commons a Covid anti-corruption
OL,8,Fprobe would go ahead, aimed at
OL,9,Fclaiming back money from Covid fraud.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Treasury, which
OL,12,Fis now leading efforts to investigate
OL,13,FCovid corruption, said: "The
OL,14,FChancellor has been clear that she
OL,15,Fwill not tolerate waste and will
OL,16,Fappoint a Covid corruption
OL,17,Fcommissioner to get back the money
OL,18,Fthat is owed to the British people.
